Prolonged release oxycodone-naloxone for treatment of severe restless legs 
syndrome after failure of previous treatment: a double-blind, randomised, 
placebo-controlled trial with an open-label extension.

Trenkwalder C(1), Beneš H, Grote L, García-Borreguero D, Högl B, Hopp M, Bosse 
B, Oksche A, Reimer K, Winkelmann J, Allen RP, Kohnen R; RELOXYN Study Group.

