M, Leibinger R, Luer W, Lunser W, Mahler A, Mattern W, Mayer G, Molt W, Oertel 
W, Peglau I, Peltz J, Ruttgers E, Sallach K, Scholl I, Schulze A, Schumann V, 
Siefjediers V, Siever A, Sigel KO, Simonow A, Sixel-Doring F, Sloksnat R, Sommer 
