The objective of this paper was to study the in vitro and in vivo inhibitory 
effect of Bidens bipinnata L. extract on growth of cervical carcinoma U14 cells. 
MTT method was used to determine the inhibitory effect of Bidens bipinnata L. 
extract on U14 tumour cells, and the effects of Bidens bipinnata L. extract on 
inhibition rate of solid tumour and life prolongation rate of ascites tumour 
were observed through the establishment of two animal models of mouse cervical 
